t: "Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúCome! Let me recite to you what your Lord has forbidden to you: do not associate others with Him ňĻin worshipňļ. ňĻDo not fail toňļ honour your parents. Do not kill your children for fear of poverty. We provide for you and for them. Do not come near indecencies, openly or secretly. Do not take a ňĻhumanňļ life‚ÄĒmade sacred by Allah‚ÄĒexcept with ňĻlegalňļ right.¬†This is what He has commanded you, so perhaps you will understand"